# Agentstack local development values.
# Copy values into your shell for app runtime experiments only.
# For Agentstack local-cloud preview state, use `agentstack env set` and preview scripts.
# Provider execution is explicit through `agentstack provider inspect/apply`; this file is not a provider deployment source.
# For source-prototype smoke runs, set AGENTSTACK_CLI_BIN and AGENTSTACK_TSX_BIN in your shell.

